ue2

Class Biome

  • java.lang.Object
    • ue2.Biome

  • public class Biome
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a "Biome", which can store multiple numbers of Villages. It has to have a name and a kind of biome (e.g. "desert", "gras"...).
    Author:
    Paul Jureschek, Michael Kinzkofer
